    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# Template configuration\n\n## How this template works\n1. **Set project_key** holds the hardcoded key for this deployment.\n2. **Get Project Config** fetches the row from the `cs_project_config` data table.\n3. **Restore trigger data** re-emits the trigger payload so `Switch` and the four `Set *_data` nodes see `$json.requestType`, `$json.subscriptionId`, etc. as the trigger gave them.\n4. `keyID` references the table column `hmac_key_id` via `$('Get Project Config').first().json.hmac_key_id`.\n\n## To duplicate for a new project\n- Duplicate this workflow.\n- Change the value in **Set project_key**.\n- Ensure the table row for the new key has `hmac_key_id` set.\n- Re-bind the Sign payload crypto credential (HMAC secret) for the new project.",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 540,
        "color": 5
      },
